                <h3>Our Philosophy</h3>
                <ul class="feature-list">
                    <li><strong>Value of Life:</strong> Every life has value and deserves protection from the cold</li>
                    <li><strong>Practical Support:</strong> Helping restore dignity and energy by addressing basic needs</li>
                    <li><strong>Affordable Solution:</strong> Making life-saving technology accessible to those experiencing homelessness</li>
                </ul>
